lead_paragraph: Two men claiming to act on behalf of a pro-Qaddafi party and said to be seeking European visas surrendered after forcing an Afriqiyah Airways flight to change course.

byline.contributor: Suliman Ali Zway contributed reporting from Berlin, and Nour Youssef from Cairo.

headline.print_headline: Libyan Plane Lands in Malta in Peaceful End to Hijacking
headline.main: Hijacking Ends Peacefully After Libyan Airliner Lands in Malta
